OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1773990267
OL,3,CSecondary school-aged child sexually
OL,4,Cassaulted
OL,6,FA secondary-school aged child has been
OL,7,Fsexually assaulted in Bristol.
OL,9,FAvon and Somerset Police were called
OL,10,Fafter the incident took place in West
OL,11,FTown Lane in Brislington at around
OL,12,F10.30am on Tuesday 17 March.
OL,14,FThe force said specialist detectives
OL,15,Fhave met with the victim and her
OL,16,Ffamily, and will continue to support
OL,17,Fthem as the investigation progresses.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
