FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1773990267
OL,3,CSecondary school-aged child sexually
OL,4,Cassaulted
OL,6,FA spokesperson for the force said: "A
OL,7,Fscene is in place and officers are
OL,8,Fcarrying out a review of CCTV footage
OL,9,Fas they work to identify the man
OL,10,Fresponsible.
OL,12,F"He has been described as being of
OL,13,Fmixed heritage, aged approximately in
OL,14,Fhis early 20s, with braided hair and a
OL,15,Ftattoo on his left forearm.
OL,17,F"He was wearing a white hoodie, black
OL,18,Fjacket, black jogging bottoms, and
OL,19,Fblack trainers at the time of the
OL,20,Fincident."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
