OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1773990267
OL,3,CSecondary school-aged child sexually
OL,4,Cassaulted
OL,6,FNeighbourhood Sergeant, Chris Downham,
OL,7,Fsaid: "We recognise this incident will
OL,8,Fbe worrying for many people and a
OL,9,Fthorough investigation is being
OL,10,Fcompleted to identify the person
OL,11,Fresponsible.
OL,13,F"While this work continues,
OL,14,Fneighbourhood officers will be
OL,15,Fcarrying out extra patrols in the area
OL,16,Fand they will be happy to discuss any
OL,17,Fconcerns anyone may have.
OL,26,@oD@GOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
