CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1773990267
OL,3,CSecondary school-aged child sexually
OL,4,Cassaulted
OL,6,F"The wellbeing of the victim is a
OL,7,Fpriority and detectives will continue
OL,8,Fto make sure she, and her family, are
OL,9,Fkept updated and supported." He added.
OL,11,F"Officers are also in contact with her
OL,12,Fschool to ensure appropriate
OL,13,Fsafeguarding measures are in place for
OL,14,Fall pupils.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOU
