OL,3,CSecondary school-aged child sexually
OL,4,Cassaulted
OL,6,FThe force is asking anyone who
OL,7,Fwitnessed anything suspicious in the
OL,8,Farea yesterday morning, or anyone with
OL,9,Fany CCTV footage or information that
OL,10,Fcould be relevant to the investigation
OL,11,Fto contact them by calling 101, using
OL,12,Fthe reference number 5226073592.
